How to Use

To use an icon, you need to know the icon name and the icon type. In the example on the right the icon name is graduation-cap and the icon type is line.

graduation-cap line

Terminology

Note: The search terms used to index our icons are determined by FontAwesome, an American company, so some differences in terminology may be expected. For example, if nothing is coming back in your search using the term "university", try using "college" instead.
